fields.title: paracetamol
fields.description: Paracetamol is a common painkiller used to treat aches and pain. It can also be used to reduce a high temperature.

fields.title: Espumisan
fields.description: Espumisan capsules belong to a group of medicines called "gastrointestinal drugs." The active ingredient, simethicone, breaks down gas bubbles trapped in the stomach and intestines. Thus, the evolved gases are removed naturally.

fields.title: Banana
fields.description: Firms "Dole". Banana - one of the food crops, and for tropical countries the most nutritious food plant and the main export item. Ripe bananas are widely eaten around the world and are used in a wide variety of dishes.
